snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard: Petition to Get Heard FIRED from Aquaman 2?!
snippet.description:
The messiest divorce in Hollywood, the Depp vs. Heard drama continues. Now a recording of Amber Heard admitting that she hit Johnny Depp has cast some doubt on her story, and more people seem to be siding with Depp. Some Depp supporters are calling for Amber Heard to get canceled from 'Aquaman 2.'
